HEADWORD: Supposable
<hw>Sup*pos"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Capable of being
supposed, or imagined to exist; <as>as, that is not a
<ex>supposable</ex> case</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Sup*pos"a*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>Sup*pos"a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

